Write a simple, generic, dependency-free webcomponent that display an animation from a sprite sheet.
The component should take as parameters:
- the sprite sheet url
- the width & height of the sprite sheet
- the number of rows in the sprite sheet
- the number of columns in the sprite sheet
- the fps of the animation, with a default of 4fps

The web component name is `sprite-sheet-animation`.

Write only the web component.

Add a comment above the web component with an example usage.

Output ONLY A SINGLE JAVASCRIPT FILE, named index.js.

If you have important precision about using the code, write it at the top of the file as a comment.
